<h4 id="kata-showmun">Kata Showmun</h4>

<p>Dalam Kamus Bahasa Arab Al-MaέΑβany [<sup id="fnref:almaany_showmun" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:almaany_showmun" class="footnote">1</a></sup>] disebutkan mengenai kata shoum(un): Artinya:</p>

