  </li>
</ul>

<h3 id="kata-shooma">Kata Shooma</h3>

<p>Dari Kamus Al-MaέΑβany tertulis beberapa arti kata <em>shooma</em> [<sup id="fnref:almaany_shooma" role="doc-noteref"><a href="#fn:almaany_shooma" class="footnote">3</a></sup>], artinya:</p>

<ul>
